OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWindy and often cloudy, with a
OL,6,Ffew showery outbreaks of rain in the
OL,7,Fnorth. Showers will ease back to
OL,8,Fhigher ground through the afternoon,
OL,9,Fleaving most areas dry and bright with
OL,10,Foccasional sunny spells. Feeling cool.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FWinds will gradually ease
OL,13,Fthrough the evening, allowing any
OL,14,Fresidual cloud to dissipate and lead
OL,15,Fto a dry night with largely clear
OL,16,Fskies.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FGenerally fine and dry with
OL,19,Flight winds. Bright though staying
OL,20,Frather cloudy through the day. Turning
OL,21,Fwarmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
