OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,6,Fbut increasingly cloudy on Monday,
OL,7,Fsome possible rain late. Breezy and
OL,8,Fcloudier on Tuesday and Wednesday,
OL,9,Fwith outbreaks of rain at times,
OL,10,Fperhaps locally heavy. Warm Monday and
OL,11,FTuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
